Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.01,1:17:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this lecture going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.51,1:17:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going on for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.51,1:17:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is this auditorium here?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.25,1:17:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's here for your comfort.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.06,1:18:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.32,1:18:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole world is here just for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.72,1:18:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you have to see beyond the egocentric what that means,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.36,1:18:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that it's here for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.13,1:18:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of divine intention, that which is here is here for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.02,1:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the divinity of all that exists shines forth.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:22.28,1:18:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,With the constant spiritual work, you see the divinity,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.43,1:18:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the essence of all that exists,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.14,1:18:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is divinity itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.94,1:18:35.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All you're seeing is divinity in its expression as this stage,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.85,1:18:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in its expression as this talking body here,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.31,1:18:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity in its expression as the flowers,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.60,1:18:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity as a Diet Pepsi,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.21,1:18:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity as a wonderful wife,
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.31,1:18:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,divinity as a Kleenex.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.39,1:18:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you have a Kleenex available?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.81,1:19:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because God wants you to have a Kleenex available.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.52,1:19:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why else?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.92,1:19:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If God didn't want you to have a Kleenex,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.84,1:19:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,there wouldn't be any Kleenexes.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.96,1:19:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't pass the Kleenex test.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.27,1:19:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness is therefore a goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.32,1:19:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.23,1:19:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, spiritual friends and groups.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.43,1:19:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The alignment with spiritual friends and groups itself
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.30,1:19:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,has a positive karmic effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.46,1:19:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The effect of a spiritual group is very powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:38.97,1:19:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,People don't realize.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.96,1:19:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't realize how powerful it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.96,1:19:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's well known in certain circles,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.96,1:19:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,such as, for instance, Alcoholics Anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.96,1:19:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,A person does very well in the energy field of AA,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.96,1:19:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,which of course is 570 and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.96,1:19:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They do very well.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.96,1:19:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And so they say,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.96,1:19:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,well, I don't need AA anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:56.96,1:19:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just go out on my own.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.00,1:20:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And next thing you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:00.00,1:20:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,they're back in the bar saying,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:01.00,1:20:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,poor me, poor me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:03.00,1:20:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the field supports you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.00,1:20:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The field supports you.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.00,1:20:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,A group like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.89,1:20:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,as a very powerful energy field,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.89,1:20:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,its intention is extremely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:14.89,1:20:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And the collective intention is overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:16.89,1:20:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So a group like this literally affects
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.89,1:20:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness level of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.89,1:20:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,which sounds egoistic to the ego.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.89,1:20:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But when you realize the power of a group like this,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.11,1:20:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you see that it extends and benefits all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.31,1:20:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This group here benefits all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.31,1:20:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you have permission to ask this question?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.03,1:20:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual energy of this group here present
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.61,1:20:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,is positively affecting all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.61,1:20:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So just what you have become,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.47,1:20:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,what you are,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.60,1:20:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,not what you do or what you have or what you own,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.60,1:21:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:01.80,1:21:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do you influence all of mankind
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.80,1:21:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,by becoming the most advanced,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:09.88,1:21:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually advanced and aware creature that you can be?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.88,1:21:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You serve all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.01,1:21:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Including God by being as spiritually evolved
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.01,1:21:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as you are capable of being.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.01,1:21:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:22.01,1:21:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of mankind benefits.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.38,1:21:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't see yourself as wanting,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.38,1:21:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,lacking or incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.38,1:21:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That which you are now is complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.56,1:21:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't move from incomplete to complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.85,1:21:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You move from complete to complete to complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.85,1:21:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely all that I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.07,1:21:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely all that I am now right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.07,1:21:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I am all that I can be.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.07,1:21:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you move from complete to complete to complete
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.36,1:21:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to be sweeter, more loving,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.88,1:22:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,more generous, more adoring
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.84,1:22:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,than I am right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:06.18,1:22:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be so.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:08.18,1:22:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me keys.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.42,1:22:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me keys, baby, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.50,1:22:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And the winner is...
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.73,1:22:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,From complete to complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.73,1:22:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Because when you have all that you could possibly want,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.73,1:22:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't go from incomplete to complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.44,1:22:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're completely all that you can be right now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.44,1:22:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And then maybe next year
Dialogue: 0,1:22:38.51,1:22:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be completely all that you can be next year
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.51,1:22:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,with a new car.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.51,1:22:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's just what completion is there.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.60,1:22:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what it is here
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.60,1:22:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's not where it'll be 10 years from now.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.60,1:22:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part of being complete
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.60,1:22:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is having what you need,
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.60,1:22:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,what you'd like, etc.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.60,1:22:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Go from complete to complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.80,1:22:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't go from lack to fulfillment.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.80,1:23:04.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You go from fulfillment to fulfillment.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:04.34,1:23:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could be taller, handsomer, and richer,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.34,1:23:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I would be.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:09.72,1:23:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.72,1:23:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Tall, dark, and handsome. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.72,1:23:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So in doing this,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.81,1:23:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you end up identifying with the self,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.07,1:23:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the large self.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.07,1:23:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now the large self
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.07,1:23:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,is infinite and perfect
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.07,1:23:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and beyond all time.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.07,1:23:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And it is beyond imperfection.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.43,1:23:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So you identify that this is my reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.88,1:23:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.90,1:23:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The self with a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.90,1:23:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is only my temporary expression
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.35,1:23:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in this domain.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.55,1:23:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The self is complete and needs nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.35,1:23:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's beyond time.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.35,1:23:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-fulfilling.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.96,1:23:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of God
Dialogue: 0,1:23:59.60,1:24:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,has love itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:01.85,1:24:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Without the presence of God within you,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.85,1:24:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.27,1:24:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.27,1:24:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,this owes its existence
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.27,1:24:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.50,1:24:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And humility is when this
Dialogue: 0,1:24:14.50,1:24:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,self begins to acknowledge
Dialogue: 0,1:24:16.50,1:24:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,that this is its source.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:18.50,1:24:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is its source.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.50,1:24:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite self
Dialogue: 0,1:24:22.77,1:24:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,with no beginning and no end.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:27.52,1:24:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember when I fell into that state
Dialogue: 0,1:24:29.52,1:24:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in a snowbank once
Dialogue: 0,1:24:31.81,1:24:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,in Wisconsin,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.81,1:24:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a million miles from nowhere in a storm.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.06,1:24:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And I shoveled the snow out of the way
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.06,1:24:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to get out of the wind,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.06,1:24:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I climbed in this hole
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.06,1:24:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,just to get out of the wind.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.47,1:24:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And then an infinite presence
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.47,1:24:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of infinite love
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.47,1:24:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,with no beginning and no end
Dialogue: 0,1:24:50.18,1:24:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,was no different than that which I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.81,1:24:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That which I am always existed,
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.81,1:24:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,will always exist.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.81,1:24:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It has no beginning and no end.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.81,1:25:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I began to realize
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.81,1:25:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,that love was eternal,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.81,1:25:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and that love was what I was.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:05.81,1:25:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Eternal love was my identity.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.81,1:25:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That came as a revelation
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.81,1:25:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,all of its own
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.81,1:25:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,without a single thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.81,1:25:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Without a single thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.88,1:25:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And also in that state,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.88,1:25:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you have permission to leave the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.88,1:25:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,So I've had,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:22.88,1:25:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,every time that's recurred,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.88,1:25:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had permission to leave the world
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.88,1:25:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,goes with it.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.88,1:25:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no reason further to continue
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.88,1:25:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,on a physical existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.88,1:25:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You can leave if you wish.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:34.88,1:25:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You have complete permission to expire.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.88,1:25:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:38.90,1:25:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Each time there was something that I was,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.90,1:25:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,for the sake of the love of someone,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.90,1:25:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I declined the offer.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.90,1:25:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's recurred over and over.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.97,1:25:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You have permission to leave the world,
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.97,1:25:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and the knowingness of the reality
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.39,1:25:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which you are
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.39,1:26:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,is the presence of God within you,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:03.15,1:26:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,complete to complete.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.26,1:26:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,The Self with a capital S.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.26,1:26:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Being happy to be here
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.52,1:26:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,when you realize that, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:12.52,1:26:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you could actually leave if you wanted to,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.52,1:26:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,except the limitations of humanness.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:17.52,1:26:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Humanness.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.03,1:26:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your protoplasm.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.64,1:26:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You've chosen to learn what can be learned
Dialogue: 0,1:26:25.64,1:26:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,only in the world of protoplasm.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.64,1:26:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So humanness has a protoplasmic,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.64,1:26:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,the karma of protoplasm.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:33.64,1:26:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.47,1:26:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,humanness is a temporary condition
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.47,1:26:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,of protoplasmic awareness,
Dialogue: 0,1:26:43.47,1:26:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,things that can only be learned
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.47,1:26:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,within the limited domain.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.77,1:27:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The word I want for it is...
Dialogue: 0,1:27:01.06,1:27:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.90,1:27:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Except the limitations of humanness.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.32,1:27:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be a human.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.32,1:27:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay to be human.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.42,1:27:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the limitations of humanness.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.71,1:27:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.71,1:27:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,to be human.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:27.28,1:27:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:30.89,1:27:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:27:36.78,1:27:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't pay any attention
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.78,1:27:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to the man behind the screen.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:49.92,1:27:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness is an intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.35,1:27:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an intention
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.35,1:27:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that you wish to be happy
Dialogue: 0,1:27:58.35,1:28:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and not make it dependent on happiness.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.42,1:28:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy if I get that car.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:03.42,1:28:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy if I get that promotion.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:05.42,1:28:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be happy if I get
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.57,1:28:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,a fried egg sandwich.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:11.06,1:28:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness is an overall intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.38,1:28:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One way to get there
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.73,1:28:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is reflection versus impulsivity.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:20.73,1:28:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Meditation is a wonderful
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.72,1:28:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual technique,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:29.03,1:28:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's limited.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.32,1:28:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's limited.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.32,1:28:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't drive your car
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.32,1:28:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and also be in a meditative state.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.32,1:28:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So being reflective.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:40.39,1:28:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflect versus impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:43.39,1:28:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you move through the world
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.39,1:28:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and make decisions,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.39,1:28:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you become increasingly reflective
Dialogue: 0,1:28:51.42,1:28:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,of all the nuances and the implications
Dialogue: 0,1:28:54.42,1:28:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and the overall spiritual context.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.42,1:28:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoughtful rather than critical.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.64,1:29:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can always find something to criticize.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:02.97,1:29:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can always find something to criticize.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:04.97,1:29:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a good time criticizing the snow
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.97,1:29:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and criticizing the wind.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.97,1:29:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, this place is windy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:11.97,1:29:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, it's blowing my hair off.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:14.97,1:29:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Critical of the weather.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.97,1:29:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I figure that's a good thing
Dialogue: 0,1:29:19.18,1:29:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,for a human being to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.18,1:29:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Complain about the weather.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:22.18,1:29:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Too hot, it's too cold, it's too windy,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.11,1:29:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,it's too breezy.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:28.11,1:29:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can enjoy the downside
Dialogue: 0,1:29:30.22,1:29:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of being a human
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.22,1:29:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and then realize
Dialogue: 0,1:29:32.22,1:29:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,it's not really a downside.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.22,1:29:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Any good human being
Dialogue: 0,1:29:35.43,1:29:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,should complain about
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.43,1:29:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,wind blowing your hat off all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.81,1:29:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand up for being a human.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.22,1:29:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have come here to complain.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:47.22,1:29:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Brave, courageous, and honest.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:53.56,1:29:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am here to complain about the weather,
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.56,1:30:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,here to complain about taxes.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.10,1:30:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We need a protest group for something.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.14,1:30:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflective rather than impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:09.27,1:30:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoughtful rather than critical.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:11.27,1:30:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Be content instead of complaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.55,1:30:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I say be content with complaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.55,1:30:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why shouldn't I be complaining?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.81,1:30:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Be content.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.10,1:30:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to cross out instead of
Dialogue: 0,1:30:28.35,1:30:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and put with complaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:32.93,1:30:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Any human worth his soul
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.85,1:30:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to complain.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:38.85,1:30:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell you who doesn't complain
Dialogue: 0,1:30:40.85,1:30:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't worth the bother.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.55,1:30:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you care about life,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.42,1:30:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll complain about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:48.42,1:30:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,One reason for complaining
Dialogue: 0,1:30:50.42,1:30:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is because you care about life.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.42,1:30:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't care about life,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.42,1:30:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't complain.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.42,1:30:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't complain about the neighborhood
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.42,1:31:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,if you don't live there.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.42,1:31:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So be content instead of complaining
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.42,1:31:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is a goal.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.47,1:31:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And realize that life is a learning curve.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:08.47,1:31:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're someplace on the curve.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:10.47,1:31:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not perfect,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:12.47,1:31:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,nor are you completely an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:14.47,1:31:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is a learning curve.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:16.51,1:31:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So be willing to accept
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.60,1:31:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.97,1:31:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Move on to the next.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.97,1:31:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I get angry and have a fit.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.97,1:31:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.35,1:31:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why aren't they moving?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.98,1:31:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is wrong with this world?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.98,1:31:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention, please.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:40.65,1:31:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:44.61,1:31:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Happiness is a destination and a direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:48.15,1:31:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Reflective versus impulsive.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.15,1:31:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thoughtful rather than critical.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.36,1:31:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Be content instead of complaining.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:59.03,1:32:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And realize life is a learning curve.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.11,1:32:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I thank all of you who quickly prayed.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:15.93,1:32:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,These are the spiritual techniques
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.57,1:32:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that we have used.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:20.57,1:32:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray for help.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:22.77,1:32:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And you ask yourself,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:23.77,1:32:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,does praying do any good?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:26.22,1:32:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I just talking to myself?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:28.22,1:32:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a gnome.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:31.90,1:32:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,A tall gnome.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:34.52,1:32:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Six foot, over six foot high gnome.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:36.52,1:32:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's actually a midget,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:38.80,1:32:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's a tall,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.80,1:32:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the tallest midget on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:41.80,1:32:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the shortest giant on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:46.81,1:32:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the tallest midget.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:49.53,1:32:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm the shortest giant.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:51.53,1:32:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.85,1:32:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Praying helps a lot.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:58.73,1:33:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, is praying wishful thinking?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:01.93,1:33:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it, you know, grade school,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.06,1:33:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,kindergarten stuff?
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.06,1:33:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have permission to...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:09.09,1:33:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Praying is beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:12.27,1:33:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Benefits yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.89,1:33:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Benefits loved ones.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.50,1:33:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Benefits the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.65,1:33:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Benefits all of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:22.01,1:33:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist. Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:24.01,1:33:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So praying is not just a
Dialogue: 0,1:33:27.51,1:33:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,grade school exercise.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:30.98,1:33:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:32.98,1:33:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:35.09,1:33:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,praying actually is an expression
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.09,1:33:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,of what you have become.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:39.09,1:33:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You've become gracious.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.09,1:33:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that you thank the Lord
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.09,1:33:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,for all the gifts of this day,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:45.09,1:33:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,both seen and unseen.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.09,1:33:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And you ask for God's direction
Dialogue: 0,1:33:49.09,1:33:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,in your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.25,1:33:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And dedicate all your actions
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.25,1:33:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,towards divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:33:54.25,1:33:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:56.25,1:33:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One of its expressions is creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:58.25,1:34:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And part of creation is human,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.31,1:34:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,humankind.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:02.31,1:34:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So pray kind of played.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.60,1:34:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Affirm God is my source.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:06.60,1:34:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Both my source and my inspiration
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.60,1:34:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and my solution.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.60,1:34:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And you sing an inner song.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:12.94,1:34:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, be happy.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.21,1:34:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing an inner song.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.21,1:34:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing an inner song.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.21,1:34:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sing an inner song.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:29.27,1:34:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You hear a child sitting there.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.27,1:34:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Happily in their high chair.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:35.43,1:34:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They got mush all over their face.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.43,1:34:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mush all over their lap.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:41.50,1:34:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And they're just going.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:48.40,1:34:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now inside of you there is still
Dialogue: 0,1:34:52.01,1:34:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the inner child.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.03,1:34:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So one way to be happy is to speak
Dialogue: 0,1:34:56.03,1:34:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,to your inner child.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:00.48,1:35:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And parent it.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.48,1:35:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So you go.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:08.56,1:35:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum hum.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.85,1:35:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum hum hum hum.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.14,1:35:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum hum.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:17.06,1:35:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum hum.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.42,1:35:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum hum.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.61,1:35:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum hum.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:21.71,1:35:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum hum.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.13,1:35:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,arm fout
Dialogue: 0,1:35:43.55,1:36:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hum hum hum
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.03,1:36:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,hum hum hum hum.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.85,1:36:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't get good at it.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.02,1:36:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You can teach your inner child
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.13,1:36:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to hum all the time then of course the inner mother says don't be humming out like like that
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.42,1:36:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,in church and in the grocery store you say you learn how to hum quietly even finally your mother
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.32,1:36:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,says stop that people are going to think you're mental or something so you learn how to hum to
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.11,1:37:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,yourself without making any noise i'm still humming even when i'm talking in the back of my mind
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.46,1:37:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,there i'm humming firm god is my source and my solution and sing an inner song
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.22,1:37:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and when if you're feeling down this is what you need you can put this on your
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.64,1:38:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,mirror where you put yourself together in the morning and it says yours is the saddest story
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.26,1:38:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,i've ever heard
Dialogue: 0,1:38:04.18,1:38:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.34,1:38:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,self-pity people love self-pity instead of criticizing yourself for self-pity
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.53,1:38:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,enjoy it yours is the saddest story you've gone and lost your thumb for christ's sake
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.02,1:38:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,i'm not even ready to leave this world and the thumb is going ahead of me
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.53,1:38:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,i go to heaven there's the thumb waiting for me saying where have you been for god's sake i've
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.57,1:38:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,been waiting here for
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.42,1:38:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,15 minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.72,1:38:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,15 minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.73,1:39:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,45 years for you to get here that is sad poor old thumb oh yeah darn it so i can have a temper
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.17,1:39:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,tantrum temper tantrum and self-pity are good insist on being miserable and gloomy oh happiness
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.11,1:39:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,is not going to do any good anyway what what good is happiness you can be happy and get run over the
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.93,1:39:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,next day
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.30,1:39:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you can be happy you don't pay your income tax they put you away you can be happy you go over
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.18,1:40:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the speed limit they give you a ticket what's there to be happy about it's better to be miserable
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.85,1:40:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and gloomy nobody will interfere with you however when things get bad number 75 now number 75 i do
Dialogue: 0,1:40:22.52,1:40:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,with myself at home i don't see very well in here i don't see very well in here i don't see very well in
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.06,1:40:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,here i don't see very well in here i don't see very well in here so i
Dialogue: 0,1:40:28.97,1:41:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,you
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.93,1:41:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,well okay
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.27,1:41:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's sort of movies i just got out of honeymoon and got out of
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.72,1:41:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,i with my business and i got out of home to west bend um so i was heading south just to go awカ
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.64,1:41:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,me west bend um so i figured for about three weeks i was like oh my god oh my god who should i hear to
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.27,1:41:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,David. Oh, poor drapey boy. Whoa. You, you have a sad, sad story. Every year you're a year older.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.57,1:41:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus Christ, what more can I say? Creeping, old age is creeping up on you. Creeping. I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.44,1:42:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you creeping. All right. Make faces at yourself in the mirror. That is a very good one.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:10.10,1:42:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You stop taking yourself so seriously. You see all the options that open up to you,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.03,1:42:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's a wonderful spiritual practice. It's a spiritual technique. The holy church of the
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.39,1:42:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,giggles. The holy church of giggledom. The way to God through giggles. If you practice all these
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.36,1:43:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,things, you'll be grateful for the gift of life. Why? Because you really enjoy life. It's easy to
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.96,1:43:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,be grateful if you enjoy it. It's easy to be grateful if you enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.15,1:43:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let your inner kid loose, if you are fearless and spontaneous, and you're loving
Dialogue: 0,1:43:11.81,1:43:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,towards everything that you encounter throughout the day, you end up feeling grateful for the gift
Dialogue: 0,1:43:19.60,1:43:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,of life. How else could I express my love for everyone present in this audience except by being
Dialogue: 0,1:43:26.21,1:43:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,here? It's only by being here and jabbering away and enjoying your presence. What a wonderful time.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:37.90,1:43:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So to be all that you can be to everyone all the time, either physically present or not
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.72,1:43:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,necessarily physically present, to be all that you can be to life. If nothing else, you reflect
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.25,1:44:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,back to life, its beauty, that life knows that you are recognizing its beauty. And when you walk
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.22,1:44:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,through the woods, the woods, the trees, realize that you are recognizing the beauty of life.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.39,1:44:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The divinity of your essence. The trees actually know it. The trees are actually aware in a
Dialogue: 0,1:44:19.69,1:44:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,non-verbal, contextual knowingness. Resist. Hmm? Huh? Oh, then I'll finish it up in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:38.32,1:44:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's the most important one. Make face in the mirror. Be grateful. Live one day at a time.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:46.36,1:44:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yesterday's gone forever, and tomorrow never gets here, because tomorrow is going to be tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:44:51.72,1:44:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:53.17,1:45:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So live only today. Be your own best friend. Expansion versus diminution of problems.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:04.88,1:45:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Diminished problems, they're all nothing. Clarify confusion of self with social role.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:10.96,1:45:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Play the role of martyr. Am I playing the role of martyr? Am I an injustice corrector? Oh,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.07,1:45:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,how the world loves injustice corrector. Oh, look how they do me wrong. The moral high ground.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:21.30,1:45:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the moral high ground. Oh, look how the world is mistreating me.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.23,1:45:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of everything. My age, my sex, my color, my religion, my country I live in. Oh, look how the world is
Dialogue: 0,1:45:39.18,1:45:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,treating me unjustly. Okay, do we play the role of the hero or the role of the victim? Play the role
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.65,1:45:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of morally superior. The competition for moral superiority in this world is intense. You think
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.64,1:45:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it's money? No, it's moral superiority to make somebody wrong. Yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:59.38,1:46:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,They say you don't, say you believe in heterosexual marriage. Now you can hate them and curse them.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:08.77,1:46:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What did they, who do they think their parents were?
Dialogue: 0,1:46:15.65,1:46:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for heterosexual marriage, you wouldn't be here, idiot. Let go of the role of being an
Dialogue: 0,1:46:24.22,1:46:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,injustice collector. Let go of the role of being provocative. Stop pushing your luck. Avoid catastrophe.
Dialogue: 0,1:46:32.43,1:46:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,1:46:33.00,1:46:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,here's some lessons. Do not buy a house in the floodplain. Do not buy a house on the edge of a
Dialogue: 0,1:46:46.18,1:46:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,mud cliff. What is it? US 1 on California, the cliffs keep falling down. And they keep buying
Dialogue: 0,1:46:54.30,1:46:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,houses right on the edge of the cliff. Sooner or later, it rains for a week and your mud in your
Dialogue: 0,1:46:59.65,1:47:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,house goes sliding down. Do not buy one there. Do not win the lottery. Next one. You're all aware of
Dialogue: 0,1:47:08.13,1:47:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,stop being approachable.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:27.27,1:47:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Protester. Obey the law. Be polite to police. Oh, my God. Stop demonstrating. Give up saving the world and mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,1:47:40.53,1:48:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Next slide. Give up being important. Improve yourself instead of others. For God's sake, pay your income taxes. Even the head of the United States Tax Department doesn't pay his goddamn income taxes. Smile and the world smiles with you.
Dialogue: 0,1:48:12.19,1:48:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Dedicate all actions to God. 101 ways to be happy.
