Dialogue: 0,1:48:35.78,1:48:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, we're going to go on a break. First, before we go on a break, you're going to make an announcement?
Dialogue: 0,1:48:39.13,1:48:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
